// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1903 — Mass File Rename (worldleaks)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: ec243351-0611-51af-8080-785a50874913

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
